                                <h2 class="text-center" style="font-family: Bodoni MT;color : cornflowerblue">Events upcoming for the next 7 days</h2>
                                <h4 class="text-center" style="color : grey; font-family: Courier New"> From {{ ("Now"|date('d/m/Y')) }} to
